title: Pet Friendly 2br/1ba -- 6th Floor Above Whole Foods Market
posting_body: ['Apartment 602', '38 Dolores St, San Francisco, CA, 94103', 'Call Now -', 'show contact info', 'x 35', 'OR Text', '35', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to text with us.', 'Need more information?', 'Copy this link:', '<URL>', 'The Greater Good: 38 Dolores', 'This is a 2 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 789 Sq.', 'Ft.', '38 Dolores embraces a green lifestyle where community wellness comes full circle.', 'Living walls are your art work; Whole Foods Market, your downstairs kitchen; Dolores Park, your backyard.', "It's a philosophy of focusing on the greater good, for yourself and your neighbors.", '**Pictures are a mix of different layouts, may not be of actual unit**', '**Prices of homes are subject to change, please contact property for most up to date pricing and availability**', 'Pet Policy', 'Pet Rent: $75/month for dogs under 75 lbs; $100 for dogs over 75 lbs; $50/month for up to 2 cats.', 'Pet rent covers two pets, i.e. if an applicant has two cats, we would only charge $50.', 'If an applicant has 2 different type of pets we only charge one pet rent which will always default to the greater amount.', '- Pet Deposit: There is a $500 deposit per pet.', 'This becomes part of the residents total security deposit and will not be refundable until the resident moves out.', '-There is a maximum of 2 pets allowed per apartment', 'Income Requirements:', 'Applicants must have a combined income requirement of 3x the rent.', 'Office Hours:', 'Monday-Friday: 9:00AM-5:00PM', '2hfzIRfQ']
